      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver with plenty of character? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter, offering reliable performance for anyone who appreciates a car that's been broken in and is ready to work. It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it remains a solid, budget-friendly option for your transportation needs!",
