    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are fully functional and have been regularly serviced, but you will notice some cosmetic wear on the exterior body and the interior upholstery. It is a solid choice for someone looking for dependable transportation who doesn't mind a few minor dings or surface imperfections. All major systems are operational, but the car is sold as-is reflecting its current state.",
