    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in an elegant Eminent White Pearl finish. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and remains in excellent mechanical shape, offering the smooth, quiet ride that Lexus is renowned for. The exterior retains a deep luster, though a careful eye will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway commuting\u2014purely cosmetic and typical for its age. Inside, the Parchment leather interior has been kept exceptionally clean; the seats are supple with no tears, and the cabin remains a strictly non-smoking environment. All premium features, including the heated and ventilated front seats, dual-zone climate control, and the intuitive navigation system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the V6 engine runs flawlessly, backed by a complete service history of regular synthetic oil changes. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turnkey luxury SUV that perfectly balances sophisticated comfort with legendary longevity, ideal for a buyer who values a well-cared-for vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
